      "content": "thanks. i just wonder about the \"agitated\" part for patient 2. u mentioned stress-induced or respiratory, but in an ER setting, do u think there's any reason to consider substance use or behavioral issues as a primary diagnostic for him vs the first guy? just trying to see if we need to prep different protocols.",
